headline: Can IonQ's (IONQ) New Leadership Shape Customer Adoption Amid the Quantum Race?
summary: IonQ announced that Scott Millard, a technology executive with a background in leading multibillion-dollar AI sales teams at Dell Technologies, has been appointed as Chief Business Officer, succeeding Rima Alameddine and reporting to CEO Niccolo de Masi.
